        <span class="section-label exodus-label">Our Services</span>
        <h2 class="section-title exodus-section-title">Professional Translation Services Across Four Practice Areas</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-3 grid--auto-fit services-grid exodus-services-grid">
        <article class="service-card exodus-service-card">
          <div class="service-image">
            <img src="/images/onedrive/tiles/tile-courts.png" alt="Legal Translation Services" loading="lazy">
          </div>
          <div class="service-content">
            <h3>LEGAL & CORPORATE</h3>
            <p>Contracts, court judgments, corporate governance, powers of attorney, and litigation documents with MOJ certification.</p>
            <a href="/services/legal-translation/" class="service-link exodus-link">Explore <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
