          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="service-card exodus-service-card">
          <div class="service-image">
            <img src="/images/onedrive/services/services-4.jpg" alt="Attestation & MOFAIC" loading="lazy">
          </div>
          <div class="service-content">
            <h3>ATTESTATION SERVICES</h3>
            <p>Document attestation for MOFA and government entities. Complete legalization services including secure courier handling.</p>
            <a href="/services/attestation/" class="service-link exodus-link">Explore <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="service-card exodus-service-card">
          <div class="service-image">
            <img src="/images/onedrive/services/services-5.jpg" alt="Certificate Translation" loading="lazy">
          </div>
          <div class="service-content">
            <h3>BUSINESS LOCALIZATION</h3>
            <p>Website and app localization, marketing adaptation, menu translation, and technical documentation for UAE market entry.</p>
            <a href="/services/certificate-translation/" class="service-link exodus-link">Explore <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="service-card exodus-service-card">
          <div class="service-image">
            <img src="/images/onedrive/tiles/tile-corporate.png" alt="Location Services" loading="lazy">
          </div>
          <div class="service-content">
            <h3>LOCATION SERVICES</h3>
            <p>On-site collection and delivery across Dubai, Abu Dhabi, and Northern Emirates. Doorstep service for busy professionals.</p>
            <a href="/locations/" class="service-link exodus-link">Explore <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="service-card exodus-service-card">
          <div class="service-image">
            <img src="/images/onedrive/tiles/tile-immigration.png" alt="Golden Visa Translation" loading="lazy">
          </div>
          <div class="service-content">
            <h3>GOLDEN VISA</h3>
            <p>Complete document packages for UAE Golden Visa applications. Academic, professional, and investment documentation.</p>
            <a href="/services/golden-visa-translation/" class="service-link exodus-link">Explore <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Choose Us Section -->
  <section id="why" class="section bg-light why-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-label">Why Choose Us?</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">The Risk Management Standard<br>for Legal Translation Services in Dubai</h2>
        <div class="section-divider"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-4 grid--auto-fit why-grid">
        <article class="why-card">
          <i class="fas fa-gavel"></i>
          <h3>MOJ Certified</h3>
          <p>UAE Ministry of Justice certified legal translation accepted by all courts and government entities.</p>
        </article>
